      "title": "Academic activities at Uva Wellassa University temporarily halted",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In-person academic activities at the University of Uva Wellassa have been temporarily from today (June 29) until further notice.",
        "Vice-Chancellor of the University, Prof. Jayantha Lal Rathnasekara said the decision was taken due to the prevailing fuel shortage."
      ],
